config IWLWIFI
    tristate "Intel Wireless WiFi Link Driver"
    default m
    help
      Support for Intel wireless adapters including:
      - WiFi 6 (802.11ax): AX200, AX201, AX210, AX211
      - WiFi 5 (802.11ac): 9560, 9260, 8265, 8260, 7265
      
      Very common in business laptops and desktops.

